textBeforeTable: Coming soon.... Coming soon.... After being hidden from the world because of false accusation's, the KGC couldn't take it any more. The KGC started rebuilding their organization once again, but with a different approach. The world saw us as heroes and then assassins, so we think why not be both. We are all over the city, people just don't realize that we are planning our resurrection and avenging George Bickley's unforgiven death, our target's are scattered in the city like insects. But we also help those who need someone taken care of, if you want to join look for the application below and fill it out. If you have a contract for the KGC just go to the events section and look for KGC Contracts. George Bickley (Feb. 21 1819 - Aug. 15 1867) As the years pass by, the KGC has been expanding and fighting against slavery. During the Civil War, the KGC were a big part of it help the Union.
